query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('amazon-ecs',
'child-process',
'connect',
'continuous-deployment',
'datacontext',
'datastax-enterprise',
'deep-linking',
'iad',
'osx-lion',
'prometheus',
'scalatest',
'social-networking');
